comment: Jordan (LAC) firms up his position and sets the screen on Hill (UTA).
Ingles (UTA) and Paul (LAC) briefly engage and separate off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Hood (UTA) lifts his pivot foot prior to starting his dribble.
Mbah a Moute (LAC) makes marginal contact with Hood (UTA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) makes marginal contact with Ingles (UTA) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Crawford (LAC) makes incidental contact with Johnson (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Jordan (LAC) sets the screen on Hill (UTA) and absorbs the contact.
Ingles (UTA) is in a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Jordan (LAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Hill (UTA).
Mbah a Moute (LAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Johnson (UTA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Paul (LAC) dislodges Favors (UTA), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Correctly called delay of game violation.
Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Johnson (UTA).
[Incidental or immaterial] Paul (LAC) grabs and pulls Hill's (UTA) jersey.
